text: Jorge Parra Sánchez (born March 14, 1994 in Guadalajara, Jalisco) is a Mexican professional footballer who last played for Inter Playa del Carmen. He made his professional debut with Guadalajara during a Copa MX victory over Mineros de Zacatecas on 5 August 2015. ==References== Category:1994 births Category:Living people Category:Mexican footballers Category:Association football defenders Category:C.D.
